trailingComments.value:
*
 * Options that are used to modify the change operation in JSONStoreCollection.

*
     * Constructor
     * @param {boolean} [addNew] - Flag to set if the document should be added if a previously stored document could not be found.
     * @param {boolean} [markDirty] - Flag to mark a document dirty. Default is false.
     * @param {Array} [searchFieldCriteria] - An Array of search fields that is used to compare in the database that is found in the document.
